MallardOrderInvitation001.name: Mallard Order Invitation 001
Letter Inscription: You have been cordially invited to become an initiate
in The Mallard Order. Are you ready to be reborn?
The Great Ceremony is almost upon us.
Do not burn your letter. This is your proof of admission.
We have been watching, and we will be watching.
